AWS is hiring a Machine Learning Software Development Engineer to help us solve complex problems in content and knowledge discovery for our customers. You will collaborate with our cross-functional team of Applied Scientists, Engineers, and Solutions Architects to research, design, develop and deploy sophisticated NLP models, design and implement infrastructure to productize the models, and build ETL pipelines to process unstructured and semi-structured data. The ideal candidate is an experienced and highly-independent software engineer, who is comfortable working on cross-functional teams. You will be able to balance technical leadership with strong business judgment to make the right decisions about technology and methodologies choices.
 
